<p>Dave&#039;s in San Jose covering WWDC, and he and John talk through all of today&#039;s announcements and what they mean to you! Then it&#039;s on to sharing some Cool Stuff Found, including a few travel-related items that Dave found on his journeys this week. Lastly, some of your questions are answered. All of this and more when you press play and enjoy.Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
